      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Web Developer specializing in modern web technologies - creating responsive websites and web applications with Laravel, Astro, and React. Exploring endless possibilities in the digital universe.
